Newmont  one of the world’s largest gold miners, was the worst performer in the  on Tuesday, falling 9.4%.

summary: Tradr ETFs, a provider of ETFs designed for sophisticated investors and professional traders, announced that it expects to launch nine new single stock leveraged ETFs on Thursday, October 23.
